Sentencas: The performance of single-cell planar solid oxide fuel cells using coal syngas, with and without hydrogen sulfide (H2S), was studied.
Titulo: Effects of coal syngas and H2S on the performance of solid oxide fuel cells:: Single-cell tests

Sentencas: A state-of-the-art gas delivery system, data acquisition system, and test stand were designed and assembled for experimentation.
Titulo: Effects of coal syngas and H2S on the performance of solid oxide fuel cells:: Single-cell tests

Sentencas: All cells were tested at 850 degrees C with a constant current load of 14.3 A (current density of 0.20 A cm(-2)).
Titulo: Effects of coal syngas and H2S on the performance of solid oxide fuel cells:: Single-cell tests

Sentencas: The results from using syngas with no H2S indicated no degradation after 290 h of operation.
Titulo: Effects of coal syngas and H2S on the performance of solid oxide fuel cells:: Single-cell tests

Sentencas: After immediately injecting CO (and water) in the H-2-N-2 mixture, there was a slight tendency of improving performance (power) and then the behavior remained steady.
Titulo: Effects of coal syngas and H2S on the performance of solid oxide fuel cells:: Single-cell tests

Sentencas: On the other hand, results for the test with syngas in the presence of H2S (200-240 ppm) indicated good performance over 570 h (650 h total operation time) with 10-12.5% degradation.
Titulo: Effects of coal syngas and H2S on the performance of solid oxide fuel cells:: Single-cell tests

Sentencas: The results suggest these cells can be used for extended periods of time for syngas applications, and in the presence of H2S the cells show no major degradation.
Titulo: Effects of coal syngas and H2S on the performance of solid oxide fuel cells:: Single-cell tests
